      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        The 36 Gunas are divided into eight categories, each carrying different weights and significance:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Varna (4 points):</strong> Spiritual compatibility and life goals</li>
        <li><strong>Vashya (2 points):</strong> Mutual attraction and control</li>
        <li><strong>Tara (3 points):</strong> Health and longevity compatibility</li>
        <li><strong>Yoni (4 points):</strong> Sexual compatibility and intimacy</li>
        <li><strong>Graha Maitri (5 points):</strong> Mental compatibility and friendship</li>
        <li><strong>Gana (6 points):</strong> Temperament and nature compatibility</li>
        <li><strong>Bhakoot (7 points):</strong> Love and affection between partners</li>
        <li><strong>Nadi (8 points):</strong> Health and progeny compatibility</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        A score of 18 or above is generally considered good, while 24+ is considered excellent for marriage compatibility.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">Doshas in Matchmaking</h2>
      
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-3">Mangal Dosha (Mars Dosha)</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        Mangal Dosha occurs when Mars is placed in certain houses in the birth chart. While it's often associated with challenges in marriage, it's not necessarily a deal-breaker. Many successful marriages have partners with Mangal Dosha, and there are effective remedies available.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-3">Nadi Dosha</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        Nadi Dosha is considered when both partners have the same Nadi (Aadi, Madhya, or Antya). This is believed to affect health and progeny. However, modern astrologers often provide remedies and solutions to mitigate its effects.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
